=== Data and Artifacts (CRITICAL MLOPS EXCLUSIONS) ===

NOTE: Raw data should not be committed to Git. We assume the 'data' folder

contains the large image files downloaded from Kaggle.

data/seg_train/
data/seg_test/

Generated Data / Intermediate Features (Phase 2)

data/train_features.csv
data/baseline_metrics.txt

Persisted Models (Phase 3 and onwards)

src/models/.joblib
src/models/.h5
src/models/.pt
src/models/.pth

MLflow / Experiment Tracking artifacts (if you add this later)

mlruns/
.mlflow/

